Character creation:
    1. USER is logged in.
    2. name new character.
    3. submit and validation.
    4. create new character in CHARACTER table linked to USER.

To play an instance:
    1. USER must choose new SCENARIO, and dispatch his CHARACTERS.
        a. IF SCENARIO is CO-OP we must choose allies
        b. USER A invites friend (USER B) on FRIENDS
        c. USER B accepts invite from USER A
    2. INSTANCE is created and stored, INSTANCE begins.
    3. TURNS are taken until INSTANCE is resolved.
    4  META CHARACTER and USER data is updated. INSTANCE is destroyed

